{"tid":2478934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《鏗鏘集》「7.21 誰主真相」獲人權新聞奬大奬 港台 ： 不會領獎","createTime":"2021-04-07T12:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T12:26:23.000Z","uid":22556,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fbb40182df6de62739438fe1c6a1bf6902e1ebb3","tid":2478934,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:13:08.000Z","msg":"廣播處長李百全曾通知「2021 年度人權新聞獎」秘書處，要求將港台所有參賽作品抽起，但遭秘書處拒絕。消息人士向《立場》透露，今日（7 日）人權新聞獎得獎者陸續獲電郵通知，當中港台囊括多個奬項，電視部公共事務組的《視點 31》及《鏗鏘集》均獲奬，而蔡玉玲擔任編導的《鏗鏘集》「7.21 誰主真相」更於紀錄片組（中文），獲人權新聞奬大奬。<br />\n<br />\n港台回覆查詢時，先重申現正就各方面的運作檢討，包括檢討提名電視及電台電目參與遴選本地、內地及國際獎項的機制，在過渡期間不會參與獎項遴選。港台又指，會退出已參選的獎項提名，及不會領取相關的獎項&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4053873011364955/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F4053873011364955%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=fd10f0d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/4053873011364955/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"0508d176087f8599dc1c76b0ef2f690568e49f07","tid":2478934,"uid":41298,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:15:37.000Z","msg":"又柒出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd624323d0e97fced3ce704af43da9cf41e625b9","tid":2478934,"uid":24457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"有獎都唔拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同全世界講緊我就係打壓新聞自由"},{"pid":"1702364b2e097cd26ab504dbc890a96f1e3bdd2c","tid":2478934,"uid":47021,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:18:47.000Z","msg":"調查真相，拎大獎嘅節目監製竟然要坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乘機煲大佢 國際戰線繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecada5f3911e3e090